


**🧩 Sliding Saga – Educational Puzzle Game**

Sliding Saga is an interactive sliding puzzle game built using Java, JSP, Servlets, and HTML/CSS.
Players can choose puzzles from different categories like famous leaders, world places, cartoons, and more. Once the puzzle is solved, it reveals interesting knowledge, quotes, or fun facts related to the picture – making learning fun and engaging.


✨ Features

🖼️ Sliding Puzzle Gameplay – Rearrange tiles to solve images

🌍 Multiple Categories – Leaders, Places, Cartoons, Marvels & more

🎓 Knowledge Unlock – Get facts, quotes, or answers once the puzzle is completed

🔑 User Authentication – Secure login & registration system

📊 Interactive UI – JSP pages with smooth integration of puzzles and knowledge content

🚀 Educational + Fun – A blend of gaming and learning


🛠️ Tech Stack

Java (Servlets, JSP) – Backend logic & authentication

HTML5 / CSS3 – Frontend design and responsive layout

JDBC + DAO Pattern – Database connectivity & queries

MySQL / Any RDBMS – User and puzzle data storage


📂 Project Structure

Sliding-Saga/
│── DBConnection.java      # Handles database connection
│── DBInfo.java            # Database configuration
│── LoginDAO.java          # Data Access Object for login
│── RegisterDAO.java       # DAO for registration
│── LoginServlet.java      # Handles login requests
│── RegisterServlet.java   # Handles user registration
│── LogoutServlet.java     # Handles logout
│── UserBean.java          # Java Bean for user data
│── LoginSuccess.jsp       # Puzzle dashboard after login
│── RegSuccess.jsp         # Registration success page
│── Msg.jsp                # Display messages
│── index.html             # Landing page
│── main.html              # Puzzle play area
│── bg/                    # Background images or assets
│── README.md              # Project documentation

⚡ Getting Started

1️⃣ Clone the Repository
